FBIS4-51083 "drchi101_o_94004" FBIS-CHI-94-101 Daily Report 23 May 1994 REGIONAL AFFAIRS East Region Shanghai Shortens Taiwan Cleric's Stay Shanghai Shortens Taiwan Cleric's Stay OW2505043294 Shanghai People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 23 May 94 OW2505043294 Shanghai People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [From the "990 Morning News" program] [Text] Acting in accordance with the law, the municipal public security bureau shortened the stay of Wu Yuankun, a missionary from Taiwan's Christian Association of Sunday Schools, because he engaged in illegal activities which jeopardized social stability and normal religious activities during his stay in Shanghai. Wu returned to Taiwan by plane yesterday [23 May].
